description: This file defines a mock class for the SecureStorageService, used for unit testing gRPC server interactions. It includes mock methods corresponding to the service's RPC calls, facilitating the simulation of server behavior in tests.

classes.name: SecureStorageServiceMock
classes.description: A mock implementation of the SecureStorageService gRPC service, providing mock methods for each RPC call to facilitate testing.

methods.name: GetValue
methods.description: Mock method for the GetValue RPC, used to simulate retrieval of a secure storage value.

methods.name: UpdateValue
methods.description: Mock method for the UpdateValue RPC, used to simulate updating a secure storage value.

methods.name: DeleteValue
methods.description: Mock method for the DeleteValue RPC, used to simulate deletion of a secure storage value.

methods.name: DeleteAllValues
methods.description: Mock method for the DeleteAllValues RPC, used to simulate deletion of all secure storage values.

methods.name: SeedValue
methods.description: Mock method for the SeedValue RPC, used to simulate seeding the secure storage.
